    {
      "type": "patchouli:text",
      "title": "魔盒",
      "text": "方块形式的具现化生物。$(br)使用魔盒、在魔盒上走动、或者用弹射物击中它们都会触发与生物相关的特殊效果。"
    },
    {
      "type": "spectrum:pedestal_crafting",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier3/mob_blocks/axolotl_mob_block",
      "text": "给予短暂的生命恢复效果。"
    },
    {
      "type": "spectrum:pedestal_crafting",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier3/mob_blocks/bat_mob_block",
      "text": "高亮显示半径8格范围内的生物。"
    },
    {
      "type": "spectrum:pedestal_crafting",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier3/mob_blocks/bee_mob_block",
      "text": "为周围的植物施肥。"
    },
